{"tid":1926912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【意大利肺炎】意大利外長拍片 感謝中國提供口罩","createTime":"2020-03-15T12:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T15:57:15.000Z","uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb5410e6316371c21654f2b8ee682c91182b90a","tid":1926912,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2590000/2590585/140320_169_i_v1B_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2590000%2F2590585%2F140320_169_i_v1B_1024.jpg&h=5d96a57f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情在意大利迅速蔓延，中國自身疫情亦十分嚴重，不忘向意大利伸出援手，提供口罩、呼吸機等醫療物資。意大利外長迪馬約（Luigi Di Maio）對中國表示感謝，並斥歐洲盟國沒有表達相同的協助意願。<br />\n<br />\n迪馬約在Facebook發短片，對中方表達團結的行為表達謝意。意大利疫情嚴峻，醫療用品供應緊張之際，中國紅十字會提供30噸口罩、心肺呼吸機等物資，貨機周四抵達意大利，助解燃眉之急。<br />\n<br />\n迪馬約稱，中國並派了醫生及冠狀病毒專家，馳援意大利，強調意大利並不孤單，世上有願意幫助意大利的人。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，德國、法國等歐洲國家，都表明無意出口口罩，迪馬約暗斥歐洲盟國對意大利的幫助，反而有所不及，並指歐洲央行本應出手相助，卻未有這樣做，導致意大利股市暴瀉。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲央行日前公布議息結果，疫情陰霾下未有減息，但有增加資產購買計劃規模，並公布長期再融資操作(LTROs)，向銀行提供額外流動性，以及降低定向長期再融資操作（TLTRO III）的息率。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/todayreview88/videos/%E6%AD%A3%E8%A8%80%E6%AD%A3%E7%89%87%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E9%A6%B3%E6%8F%B4%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E8%A8%98%E5%BE%97%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E4%BD%A0%E5%80%91%E5%B9%AB%E9%81%8E%E6%88%91%E5%80%91/228557708270343/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftodayreview88%2Fvideos%2F%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E8%25A8%2580%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25B7%259D%25E9%25A6%25B3%25E6%258F%25B4%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25A8%2598%25E5%25BE%2597%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%2580%2591%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%2F228557708270343%2F&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=d0fb9b07\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/todayreview88/videos/%E6%AD%A3%E8%A8%80%E6%AD%A3%E7%89%87%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E9%A6%B3%E6%8F%B4%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E8%A8%98%E5%BE%97%E7%95%B6%E5%B9%B4%E4%BD%A0%E5%80%91%E5%B9%AB%E9%81%8E%E6%88%91%E5%80%91/228557708270343/</a>"},{"pid":"617f2c41280bb67dcf32e4d224d88d3406b0dca4","tid":1926912,"uid":216127,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:17:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92169660afbb220534b6b5115cec6e3847b9d60f","tid":1926912,"uid":184261,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:27:48.000Z","msg":"真係抵佢爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bb1bec6924c4fa090246f00b2cb0a477cce938","tid":1926912,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:18:49.000Z","msg":"三戰<br />\n中俄意葡vs美英法德<br />\n希望唔好咁快黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f00622c727df5a79b8ecc393caffe0cf7af04d9e","tid":1926912,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"13bb1bec6924c4fa090246f00b2cb0a477cce938","tid":1926912,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:18:49.000Z","msg":"三戰<br />\n中俄意葡vs美英法德<br />\n希望唔好咁快黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:20:04.000Z","msg":"英法德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ceaff7b96d9c2ff4dea29ad99ae77a92e0ea98","tid":1926912,"uid":322976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"樓主你po嘅連結係藍屍page「今日正言」<br />\n講嘅嘢最好fc下先<br />\n以下係意大利外長個fb<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/LuigiDiMaio/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLuigiDiMaio%2F&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=9959b492\" data-auto-link targ